@startuml analysis_suite
title Analysis: Health, Graph, Find, Lint

participant "Software Architect" as architect
participant "Analysis" as bausteinsicht_cli_analysis
participant "Health" as bausteinsicht_health
participant "Graph" as bausteinsicht_graph
participant "Search" as bausteinsicht_search
participant "Constraints" as bausteinsicht_constraints

architect -> bausteinsicht_cli_analysis : 1. bausteinsicht health
bausteinsicht_cli_analysis -> bausteinsicht_health : 2. score(model) across weighted categories
bausteinsicht_health --> architect : 3. health score + category breakdown
architect -> bausteinsicht_cli_analysis : 4. bausteinsicht graph ‑‑check-cycles
bausteinsicht_cli_analysis -> bausteinsicht_graph : 5. analyze(relationships): cycles, dependency depth, centrality
bausteinsicht_graph --> architect : 6. report (exit 1 if cycles found)
architect -> bausteinsicht_cli_analysis : 7. bausteinsicht find 'cache*'
bausteinsicht_cli_analysis -> bausteinsicht_search : 8. search(model, pattern) across elements/relationships/views
bausteinsicht_search --> architect : 9. matching elements
architect -> bausteinsicht_cli_analysis : 10. bausteinsicht lint
bausteinsicht_cli_analysis -> bausteinsicht_constraints : 11. evaluate(model, rules)
bausteinsicht_constraints --> architect : 12. violations (exit 1 if any)

@enduml
